high_descs: Go forward to the kitchen island, then turn left to go to the counter.
Pick up the pan on the counter.
Turn around, then turn left to go to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Turn right and go forward, then turn left of the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter then take a step to your right.
Pick up the dirty frying pan that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the counter that's in front of you and when you get to it take a step to your right.
Wash the frying pan in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn right and walk to the fridge that's on your left and when you get to it turn left to face it.
Put the pan in the fridge on the middle shelf then close the door when you're done.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean frying pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the dirty pan on the stove.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the pan in the fridge on the second shelf, below the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed pan in a fridge.
